snippet.title: Cart Life - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming in 2023! Wishlist on Steam: PlayCartLife.com

In Cart Life, you are a street vendor trying to achieve your dreams. Play as three everyday people selling newspapers, coffee, and bagels. Explore the city, build relationships, and try to balance your business with your personal needs in this new definitive version of Richard Hofmeier's award-winning retail simulator. 

Learn more at: www.adhocla.com/cartlife
